Core Capabilities
- Dynamic day-night cycle drives escalating survival pressure and enemy behavior.
- Base defense mechanics require campfire maintenance, barricading, and resource allocation.
- Cooperative rescue objectives track four missing children across large forest terrain.
- Loot collection systems support weapons, materials, fuel, and crafting progression.
- Creature AI includes aggressive entities, stealth threats, and night-specific attack patterns.

